{"tid":1327683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨咁做都係怕中國分裂姐...","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:11:13.000Z","uid":161419,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57c54046299383cb733d8a20ce8f5bf37e7760dd","tid":1327683,"uid":161419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"見到咁多感人爸媽post都想借朋友account出一出post。<br />\n<br />\n話說今日我同一個港豬親戚傾計，佢五十幾就六十歲啦，係個種典型嘅奴才性格香港人，明知共產黨係好衰，但又會幫共產黨嘅暴政搵藉口嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 共產黨改革開放咗唔係好耐，要畀啲時間佢哋，唔可以咁暴力想即刻變就變㗎。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 抗爭者抗爭咗唔係好耐，要畀啲時間你認為暴力個啲抗爭者，共產黨都立國咁多年，都改變唔切，更何況係一班十幾二十幾歲嘅年輕人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實林鄭都好慘，佢都係畀共產黨控制姐。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實新疆同西藏人都好慘，佢哋都係畀共產黨控制緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唉，有時共產黨咁做都係怕中國分裂姐...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 中國分裂咁又點呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咁咪會好似蘇聯咁解體囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 蘇聯解咗體之後，咁又點呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (又好似係喎...)<br />\n<br />\n過咗一陣...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 呀，你好似用緊小米電話，之前有人傳話，小米有後門會送你啲資料上去㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咩後門呀？上去邊呀？唔明...<br />\n<br />\n下刪一千字<br />\n我後來send 咗好多資料佢睇，跟住佢仲問我咩係DDOS，然後而加問我，要換電話換邊個牌子好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (佢原本係一啲勁勁勁慳家嘅人，十蚊八蚊都可以同人講價講勁耐，買小米純為平價)<br />\n<br />\n不過佢本身只係一種奴性心態好重，唔中意共產黨，覺得政府衰但又覺得唔應該反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。有時人就係咁，自己走入一個死胡同到思考，又或者係同溫層太強以致佢哋接收唔到其他資訊。只要有身邊人肯慢慢分析做多一步，相信唔多唔少都會影響到身邊人改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bba275ac5e918eae4c09f2e0b872856d99cf47","tid":1327683,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n但啲emoji睇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba439b96ee913281fb8150cf17a02025bec23c9","tid":1327683,"uid":161419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7bba275ac5e918eae4c09f2e0b872856d99cf47","tid":1327683,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n但啲emoji睇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次出post"},{"pid":"67cf519ab852262a2d1155c919388e719a3c6296","tid":1327683,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"多得今次我真係睇咗好多中國近代史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17be0c616020065b5053905c1bda8a2a5e2fbc9","tid":1327683,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"倪匡 談共產黨<br />\n俾 d 時間 共產黨，俾左60年 了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yJKbquy0DlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyJKbquy0DlA&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a3a86995\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yJKbquy0DlA</a>"